<!-- 규칙 추가 Window에서 월간 RadioButton 클릭하면 오른쪽 공간에 구성되는 View -->
<UserControl x:Class="TODO_List.View.AddTodo.Routine.MonthlyRoutineView"
                   xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
                   xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
    <Border>
        <Grid>
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>

            <StackPanel Grid.Row="0" Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="0,0,0,10">
                <TextBlock Text="날짜 선택: " VerticalAlignment="Center" FontWeight="Bold" Margin="0,0,5,0"/>
                <ComboBox x:Name="DayComboBox" Width="45" SelectedIndex="0"
                                 ItemsSource="{Binding Days}" SelectedItem="{Binding SelectedTempDay, Mode=TwoWay}"/>
                <Button Content="등록" Margin="5,0,5,0" Command="{Binding DateRegisterCommand}"/>
            </StackPanel>

            <Grid Grid.Row="1">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <ListBox Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="0" Style="{StaticResource MonthlySelectedDaysListBox}"
                            ItemsSource="{Binding SelectedMonthlyDates}" x:Name="SelectedDaysListBox"/>
                <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical" Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="0" VerticalAlignment="Top">
                    <Button Content="제거" Margin="5,0,0,5" Height="22.5" VerticalAlignment="Top"
                                Command="{Binding DateRemoveCommand}"
                                CommandParameter="{Binding SelectedItems, ElementName=SelectedDaysListBox}"/>
                    <Button Content="초기화" Margin="5,0,0,5" Height="22.5" VerticalAlignment="Top"
                                Command="{Binding DatesClearCommand}"/>
                </StackPanel>
                <TextBlock Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Grid.Row="1" Style="{StaticResource TextBlockItalic}"
                                Text="29, 30, 31일 선택시 해당 날짜가 존재하지 않으면 규칙이 생성되지 않습니다."
                                TextWrapping="Wrap"/>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Border>
</UserControl>